    link/loopback 00:00:00:00:00:00 brd 00:00:00:00:00:00
    inet 127.0.0.1/8 scope host lo
       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever
2: eth0: <BROADCAST,MULTICAST> mtu 1500 qdisc noop state DOWN qlen 1000
    link/ether 00:22:68:13:da:7d brd ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
3: wlan0: <BROADCAST,MULTICAST,UP,LOWER_UP> mtu 1500 qdisc mq state UP qlen 1000
    link/ether 00:1e:65:6b:ef:ca brd ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
    inet 192.168.0.62/24 brd 192.168.0.255 scope global wlan0
       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever
</pre>}}

=== Activate eth0 interface ===
{{RootCmd|ip link set eth0 up}}

=== Configure IP address on eth0 interface ===
* Add IP address to interface
{{RootCmd|ip addr add 192.0.2.1/24 dev eth0}}
* Remove IP address from interface
{{RootCmd|ip addr del 192.0.2.2/24 dev eth0}}

